	measure 'Order Hours (hh:mm)' = ```
			
			VAR OrderHrs = [Order Hours]
			RETURN 
			IF(
			    OrderHrs = 0 || ISBLANK(OrderHrs),
			    BLANK(),
			    TIME(INT(OrderHrs), MOD(OrderHrs * 60, 60), 0)
			)
			
			```
